.SH NAME
CWE\-697 \- Incorrect Comparison
.SH RANK
KEV\-referenced weakness. Not part of the 2025 CWE Top 25; documented here because it appears in the CISA KEV catalog.
.SH CLASSIFICATION
Class: KEV\-referenced weakness.
.SH DESCRIPTION
The product compares two entities in a security\-relevant context, but the comparison is incorrect, which may lead to resultant weaknesses. This Pillar covers several possibilities: the comparison checks one factor incorrectly; the comparison should consider multiple factors, but it does not check at least one of those factors at all; the comparison checks the wrong factor.
